data.description: Fantastic Commercial Property with a Charming Remodeled Home This 3/2 older home on 1.64 acres M/L has been beautifully remodeled and zoned for commercial use. It features a lot of Hwy 5 South frontage, making it an ideal location for your business. The 2054 Sq Ft main home boasts two workshops on the property, a stable, chicken coop, and a storm shelter. All of these features make it a perfect space for both living and working. This property can be yours for just $200,000.
